('Clínica Dental Raslan', 'Dental', 'Family dental clinic in Barcelona with two convenient locations in Sarrià-Sant Gervasi and Eixample. Dentists have received American Dental Association (ADA) accredited advanced specialty training at top US universities including Boston University and New York University (NYU). English-speaking environment specifically catering to international patients. Offers comprehensive dental services including dental implants, orthodontics (Invisalign certified), dental aesthetics (veneers, teeth whitening), endodontics (microscopic), periodontics (gum disease treatment), dental prosthesis, preventive dentistry, and odontopediatrics. 24-hour emergency dental service available at Plaça Tetuán location, including weekends. Tailor-made financing options available. First visit free. International insurances accepted. Gift cards and family plans available.', 'C/ Ganduxer 59 Bis, 08022 Barcelona', 'Barcelona', 'Barcelona', '+34 937 656 788', 'info@clinicaraslan.com', 'https://clinicaraslan.com/en/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
